<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/SVG Chart Streaming">
    Blazorise SVG Chart Streaming
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Append live data and keep the chart viewport moving.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    SVG chart streaming is configured with <Code>SvgChartStreamingOptions</Code>. Set <Code>Duration</Code> to a time window for rolling retention, or leave <Code>Duration</Code> as <Code>null</Code> for infinite retention.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="Append values">
        Append values through the chart reference. A timer can call the same method in a live application.
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
    <DocsPageSectionContent Code="SvgChartStreamingExample" Outlined FullWidth>
        <SvgChartStreamingExample />
    </DocsPageSectionContent>
</DocsPageSection>

